  "method": [
    "Melt the butter in a large skillet over medium-high heat. Add the bell pepper and onion and sauté for 10 minutes. Crumble in the tofu along with the prepared seitan. Sauté for 5 minutes more and add the taco seasoning and salt. Sprinkle in flaxseed meal and mix well.",
    "Spoon half the mixture into each tortilla and roll burrito-style. Cut in half and serve."
  ],
